            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab>Il <rs key="#Notary">notaio</rs> e <rs key="#Scabini">scabino</rs>
                        <persName key="#Notary #Scabini"><name ref="Giselfredus"
                            >Ghisalfridi</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Rofredus"
                                >Roffridi</name></persName> riceve in livello dal <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >vescovo</rs> di Lucca <persName ref="#people/213" key="#Bishops"
                            >Pietro</persName>, una casa et res posta in loco ubi dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/729">Castelione</placeName> prope <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/262"><rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/730">Sancti
                            Miniati</placeName></orgName> et prope <orgName
                            key="#Baptismal_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/261"><rs
                                key="#Baptismal_churches">plebe</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Baptismal_churches" ref="#places/465">Sancti
                                Genesi</placeName></orgName>, di pertinenza della <orgName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/72"><rs key="#Churches"
                                >chiesa</rs> di Santa Maria</orgName> sita loco et finibus ubi
                        dicitur <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/63">a Monte</placeName> e
                        della <orgName key="#Baptismal_churches"><rs key="#Baptismal_churches"
                                >chiesa</rs> di <placeName key="#Baptismal_churches"
                                ref="#places/152">Sant’Ippolito</placeName></orgName> qui sunt de
                        subpotestate del <orgName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/68"
                                ><rs key="#Mother_churches">vescovato</rs> di San Martino</orgName>,
                        in precedenza tenuta dal <persName>fu <name ref="Iordanus"
                            >Giordano</name></persName> e ora dal figlio, con tutte le sue
                        dipendenze. Si impegna a versare pro omni censum et iustitia al vescovo e ai
                        suoi successori per i successivi 29 anni ad ipsa ecclesie Sancte Marie il
                        censo annuale di 24 denari d’argento ad pars della stessa chiesa. Se non
                        rispetterà i suddetti impegni, promette con i suoi eredi e illas personas
                        homini cui nos suprascripta casa et res libellario nomine dederimus di
                        versare al vescovo e ai suoi successori la pena di 50 soldi d’argento.
                        Chiede al <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notaio</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Leo">Leone</name></persName> la
                        stesura di due <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum
                            <placeName key="#Mother_churches #Bishops" ref="#places/4"
                            >Luca</placeName>. <rs key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs> sottoscrittori:
                            <persName ref="#people/149" key="#Witness">Cunimundo</persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Aemilius">Emillo</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Imelfredus"
                            >Imalfridi</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Giovanni</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Ildebrandus">Ildiprando</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Vitus">Vito</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary #Scabini"><name ref="Adalbertus"
                            >Adalperto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Scabini">schabinus</rs>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
